description:
This is a 16 minute workout called '15 MIN NO REPEAT CALISTHENICS WORKOUT | Beginner Friendly' from the channel Tom Peto Training.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Follow along with this 15 minute no repeat Calisthenics workout you can do at home with no equipment. This full body workout includes some of the best Calisthenics exercises for building muscle and strength. This is a beginner friendly Calisthenics workout with easier exercise variations provided.
